know that Google has made a

01:00:02.190 --> 01:00:05.580
huge contribution to
transparency in what's in

01:00:05.580 --> 01:00:09.890
buildings, so the US Green
Building Council has had a big

01:00:09.890 --> 01:00:13.490
effort just to say what's
in a building.

01:00:13.490 --> 01:00:16.470
Shouldn't we know, and the
American Chemical Council

01:00:16.470 --> 01:00:19.890
completely squashed it in an
ugly way, and Google gave $3

01:00:19.890 --> 01:00:23.750
million to the US Green Building
Council to increase

01:00:23.750 --> 01:00:24.700
transparency.

01:00:24.700 --> 01:00:26.480
Am I saying that right?

01:00:26.480 --> 01:00:30.180
OK, and I guess some of the
people in this room--

01:00:30.180 --> 01:00:31.020
Thank you--

01:00:31.020 --> 01:00:34.270
were, in part, responsible for
this, so you guys are really

01:00:34.270 --> 01:00:37.760
contributing, and it's
really important.

01:00:37.760 --> 01:00:39.960
When someone builds a building
to be able to know what's in

01:00:39.960 --> 01:00:42.115
it, and say--

01:00:42.115 --> 01:00:44.310
and I think the example I always
give is, one of the

01:00:44.310 --> 01:00:47.590
most persistent chemicals around
are stain repellents,

01:00:47.590 --> 01:00:49.240
like they put on carpets.

01:00:49.240 --> 01:00:52.900
And I always think, if you say
to a mom, so you can have a

01:00:52.900 --> 01:00:55.440
stain repellent carpet, but when
your baby crawls on it,

01:00:55.440 --> 01:00:57.270
chemicals are going to go into
their body that they're going

01:00:57.270 --> 01:00:58.820
to be there for the rest of
their life, and they're

01:00:58.820 --> 01:01:01.740
harmful, or you can not have
such a good stain repellent.

01:01:01.740 --> 01:01:04.320
What would a mom pick, but
we're not given that

01:01:04.320 --> 01:01:08.310
information, so transparency
information, those are things

01:01:08.310 --> 01:01:09.870
we really, really
should demand.

01:01:09.870 --> 01:01:11.490
And maybe they're things
Google can help with.

01:01:11.490 --> 01:01:14.690
You're so into free information,
so maybe that's

01:01:14.690 --> 01:01:16.950
the connection of why
you gave $3 million.

01:01:16.950 --> 01:01:21.940
Really great, I hadn't thought
about that before, but I think

01:01:21.940 --> 01:01:23.760
with information--

01:01:23.760 --> 01:01:24.940
that's really smooth--
information,

01:01:24.940 --> 01:01:26.780
we can all be healthier.

01:01:26.780 --> 01:01:29.330
So anyway, the world thanks
you for that $3

01:01:29.330 --> 01:01:32.770
million, the USGBC.

